data.description: This home on a corner lot has been well-cared for, updated & won't last long! The layout is open, spacious with vaulted ceilings, tons of natural light and a modern kitchen with quartzite counter tops & new sink! Updated lighting w/dimmers, garden tub in the primary suite & plenty of room in the fenced backyard for pets, BBQs & hanging out during the summer. 3 garage spaces gives you enough space for a workshop. Practicality meets convenience in this tidy & friendly neighborhood. The best part is – no HOA! But there's more to love – this home is conveniently located with nearby walking & bike paths, hiking trails, Bodega Park Playground, shopping centers, restaurants, and medical facilities. Quick freeway access, friendly neighbors, and mature landscaping are added perks of living in the area. Don't miss the  opportunity to make this place your own! Seller may be able to accomadate showings outside of their preferred times with advance notice.
